Interface Command.Response

  • All Superinterfaces:
    Serializable
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    AddId.Response, CommandList.Response, Commands.Response, Config.Response, Count.Response, DatabaseQueryResponse, Decoders.Response, HealthResponse, Idle.Response, List.Response, ListFiles.Response, ListMounts.Response, ListNeighbors.Response, ListPlaylist.Response, ListPlaylists.Response, LsInfo.Response, Outputs.Response, PlChangesPosId.Response, QueueQueryResponse, ReplayGainStatus.Response, SimpleResponse, Stats.Response, Status.Response, TagTypes.Response, UrlHandlers.Response
    Enclosing interface:
    Command<R extends Command.Response>

    public static interface Command.Response
extends Serializable
    An interface to access data of the response. The intention is for this interface to be extended for each command to access command specific responses. Implementations of Response should be able to read the response lines for the MPD protocol response fields and access their values.
